015,0,Rear Doors (Window Regulators)
015,1,Window Regulator,Button Rear Right,Display Range: auto. open/auto. close/man. open/man. close/Not Oper./Not Installed
015,2,Window Reg. Therm.,Prot. Rear Right,Display Range: Yes/No/Not Oper.
