015,4,Window Reg. Therm.,Prot. Rear Left,Display Range: Yes/No/Not Oper.
;
016,1,Supply Voltage,(Terminal 30)
016,2,Status,Terminal 15,Display Range: Term. 15 On/Term. 15 Off
016,3,Status,S-Contact,Display Range: Activated/Not Oper.
016,4,Comfort-BUS,Condition,Display Range: 1-Wire/2-Wire
;
