;
;---------------------------------------------------
;
; coding
;
;---------------------------------------------------
;
;
C00,Comfort System (J393) Coding
C01,+00001 = Anti-Theft Warning System via Remote Control
C02,+00002 = Confirmation Anti-Theft Warning System (Blink)
C03,+00004 = Selective Central Locking (SCL)
C04,+00008 = Anti-Theft Warning System installed
C05,+00016 = Rear Lid Release Locking at 5 km/h
C06,+00032 = Central Locking at 15 km/h (or 10 mph)
C07,+00064 = Comfort Function via Remote Control
C08,+00128 = Right Hand Drive (RHD)
C09,+00512 = Confirmation for Locking via Remote Control (Blink)
C10,+01024 = Confirmation Anti-Theft Warning System (Horn)
C11,+02048 = Door/Window Regulator Logic (North America)
C12,+04096 = Confirmation for Unlocking via Remote Control (Blink)
C13,+16384 = Selective Central Locking (SCL) via Key Switch only
C14, 
C15,Note #1: Coding Value is the Sum of the individual Options!
C16,Note #2: You can also use the Coding Assist/Helper!
;
;
;---------------------------------------------------
;
; converted coding
; (short coding displayed as long coding for easier modifications)
;
;---------------------------------------------------
;
;
LC,02,0,Anti-Theft Warning System via Remote Control
LC,02,1,Confirmation Anti-Theft Warning System (Blink)
LC,02,2,Selective Central Locking (SCL)
LC,02,3,Anti-Theft Warning System installed
LC,02,4,Rear Lid Release Locking at 5 km/h
LC,02,5,Central Locking at 15 km/h (or 10 mph)
LC,02,6,Comfort Function via Remote Control
LC,02,7,Right Hand Drive (RHD)
LC,01,1,Confirmation for Locking via Remote Control (Blink)
LC,01,2,Confirmation Anti-Theft Warning System (Horn)
LC,01,3,Door/Window Regulator Logic (North America)
LC,01,4,Confirmation for Unlocking via Remote Control (Blink)
LC,01,6,Selective Central Locking (SCL) via Key Switch only
LC,01,7=,Additional Coding Options can be found in Byte 02!
LC,00,3=,Coding Details can be found in Byte 01 && Byte 02!
;
